room_title: Escape room "The Unreal Room" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: We just had our daughter's 12th birthday there last week in the NEW kid friendly escape room and the girls absolutely loved it!! They had such an awesome time and the convenience of the party room right there was just perfect! Thank you for such a memorable party experience and for creating a KIDS room they can actually escape from on their own!!

room_title: Escape room "The Unreal Room" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: we did a birthday party for our 9 year old. staff was awesome! the kids all had a great time and really got into it. we look forward to going back and checking out some of the other escape rooms

room_title: Escape room "The Unreal Room" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: Fun place! Brought our Junior Girl Scout troop ages 10-11 to the Unreal Room for kids and they all loved it! Staff was super friendly. Has a small off street parking lot which made parking a breeze. Will definitely return!
